I"r<p>In <a href="http://jest.pt/">JEST</a>, a junior enterprise providing pedagogical services in data-science, I had the opportunity to teach programming at a beginner level, with particular focus on <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">R</code> and <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Python</code>. Within <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Python</code>, apart from focusing on the basic aspect of it, I also had the opportunity to speak about more modern packages for interactive data visualization, such as <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">plotly</code>.</p>
